CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1775725560
OL,3,CThousands of illegal cigarettes,
OL,4,Cpouches and vapes seized during raids
OL,6,FNearly nine kilos of illegal tobacco,
OL,7,Falong with 13,000 illicit cigarettes
OL,8,Fhave been seized as part of series of
OL,9,Fraids in Oxfordshire.
OL,11,FThe County Council's Trading Standards
OL,12,Fteam visited seven shops across Cowley
OL,13,Fand Headington, alongside specialist
OL,14,Ftobacco detection dogs on 29 and 31
OL,15,FMarch.
OL,17,FThe team also seized 123 units of
OL,18,Fnicotine pouches and 51 single use
OL,19,Fvapes, with the total street value of
OL,20,Fthe haul estimated to be approximately
OL,21,F#7,500.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/5
