PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1775725560
OL,3,CThousands of illegal cigarettes,
OL,4,Cpouches and vapes seized during raids
OL,6,FThe council says investigations are
OL,7,Fongoing, with premises facing
OL,8,Fpotential criminal prosecution,
OL,9,Fadditional sanctions, including civil
OL,10,Ffinancial penalties, and licensing
OL,11,Freviews.
OL,13,FCouncillor Jenny Hannaby, Oxfordshire
OL,14,FCounty Council's Cabinet Member for
OL,15,FCommunity Safety: "There is no such
OL,16,Fthing as a safe cigarette, but it is
OL,17,Fstill very concerning that counterfeit
OL,18,Fversions are so widely available, sold
OL,19,Fat pocket money prices by criminals
OL,20,Fwho don't care who they sell to.
OL,26,@wD@SOU
