OL,3,CThousands of illegal cigarettes,
OL,4,Cpouches and vapes seized during raids
OL,6,FDavina Walkin, Oxfordshire County
OL,7,FCouncil's, Trading Standards
OL,8,FOperations Manager added: "The public
OL,9,Fcan help us to create a healthier and
OL,10,Fsafer Oxfordshire by being vigilant
OL,11,Fand reporting any suspicious activity,
OL,12,Fanonymously if preferred, using our
OL,13,Fhotline.
OL,15,F"The illegal tobacco criminality is
OL,16,Frelentless at the moment - but so are
OL,17,Fwe.
OL,26,@pD@[OU
